						               													<description>Ocean Slayers Board Game is a 2-4 player fully competitive, mythical, open world, euro game with a hint of luck and dice. It is set in the isles of Bermuda, full of rich treasures, powerful ruins, ancient monsters, rival captains and uncharted territories. Set out to explore Bermuda with your mighty fleet, discover a unique landscape in every game, build and grow your economy and resources and prepare for battle to defeat the mythical Kraken. Will you conquer&amp;hellip;or will you perish?!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every tile explored will offer treasure, resources and powerful items, safe passage or spawn various breeds of ancient monsters. Players and monsters roam around the board in this strategical game, which makes the waters treacherous and monster lurking at every move. Settle on resources islands and explore Bermuda to increase your wealth and territories but beware for rival captains and monster for they can cross your plans at any time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Prepare for an amazing, mythical adventure in this free roaming ocean world full of hidden dangers and fortunes. You can play Ocean Slayers over and over and no game will be the same.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
